name: Princess Leia Organa (V)
Lore: 'Captured by Jabba. Princess Leia provided a distraction for his henchbeings. Waiting for the first chance to escape. Really made Jabba''s tail wiggle.',
Text: '* Deploys free only as an escorted captive of Jabba or a bounty hunter. Your Strangle destiny draws are +1. ''Escort alone'' on Strangle is treated as ''escort''. When released, escort is lost and you may retrieve any three cards (except Strangle).',
